# Data

## Overview

This project uses publicly available Sentinel-2 satellite imagery to analyze tree canopy changes in Ottawa between 2020 and 2025.

## Data Sources

### Sentinel-2 Multispectral Imagery

- Source: Copernicus Open Access Hub / Microsoft Planetary Computer / Sentinel-2
- Resolution: 10 m
- Years:
  - 2020
  - 2025

## Derived Data

- NDVI (Normalized Difference Vegetation Index)
- Tree canopy change raster

## Folder Structure

- **raw/** — Original satellite imagery (not included in this repository)
- **processed/** — Intermediate raster products generated during analysis

## Notes

Raw imagery is excluded from this repository to reduce repository size and can be downloaded from the original data source.
